product_name: Benefit CosmeticsPrecisely, My Brow Pencil Waterproof Eyebrow Definer Mini
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsSustainable PackagingOh my WOW - precise & defined eyebrows with Benefit's Precisely, My Brow Pencil Waterproof Eyebrow Definer! Now available in a perfect 'try-me' size mini, transform shapeless, undefined brows with just a few strokes of precisely, my brow pencil.
details: DetailsBenefitsDefined eyebrowsRich, blendable colorRetractable, non-sharpen tipFeatures12 hour longwear*Waterproof***Instrumental test on 23 panelists**Instrumental test on 22 panelistsItem 2522827How To UseHold the pencil along the custom control grip. To shape brows, use longer, horizontal strokes along the base of your brow. Fill by drawing short, upward strokes in the direction of your natural hair growth.Beauty Tip: Lock your look! Layer 24-hour brow setter over precisely, my brow pencil for defined brows that last all day!IngredientsShade 3: Stearic Acid, Rhus Succedanea Fruit Wax, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Cera Microcristallina (Microcrystalline Wax), Paraffinum Liquidum (Mineral Oil), Hydrogenated Coconut Oil, Hydrogenated Palm Kernel Oil, Aluminum Hydroxide, Hydrogenated Palm Oil, Tocopherol, Talc, Lecithin, BHT. May Contain: CI 19140 (Yellow 5, Yellow 5 Lake), CI 42090 (Blue 1 Lake), CI 77007 (Ultramarines), CI 77163 (Bismuth Oxychloride), CI 77288 (Chromium Oxide Greens), CI 77289 (Chromium Hydroxide Green), CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 77510 (Ferric Ferrocyanide, Ferric Ammonium Ferrocyanide), CI 77742 (Manganese Violet), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide).Product ingredient listings are updated periodically. Before using a Benefit Product, please read the ingredient list on the packaging of your product to be sure that the ingredients are appropriate for your personal use.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Hold the pencil along the custom control grip. To shape brows, use longer, horizontal strokes along the base of your brow. Fill by drawing short, upward strokes in the direction of your natural hair growth.Beauty Tip: Lock your look! Layer 24-hour brow setter over precisely, my brow pencil for defined brows that last all day!

reviews.headline: Don't know - Ulta's poor exchange policy made me return it
reviews.comments: I accidentally ordered the wrong shade of blonde online for instore pickup. After I got it home, I realized my mistake, so the next day I took it back to the store to exchange the UNOPENED box for the correct color. They wouldn't honor the 21 days of beauty price, so instead I returned it. It was an even exchange of the exact same product - just a different color which cost the exact same price. This is a terrible company policy that makes NO sense! Ulta lost revenue and made a very long-time customer unhappy. Why?

reviews.headline: It's fine
reviews.comments: I've used Benefit brow powder for several years but my brows are sparse and its getting harder to fill them in.  I wanted a grey pencil liner. This is very dark grey and I'd prefer a lighter grey, but oh well.  I use an angled eyeliner brush to blend this out and lighten it up. Which is ok. I'm not thrilled but, I don't have a lot of choices. I may get the cool blond or light brown sooner than later.  I do like Benefit products and appreciate the choice of colors.

reviews.headline: Great eyebrow definer!
reviews.comments: I stopped in to replace my Precisely, my brow, pencil from Benefit. The young woman who helped me was very helpful! She helped me find the correct color for the one I came in for and then recommended this product as well. I ended up purchasing both so I will always have one on back up. If you need a good eyebrow designer, I would highly recommend either of them from benefit.

reviews.headline: Repeat Customer
reviews.comments: The only brow pencil I've used for approximately 4 years. Living where summer temps reach 90⁰ to 100⁰ and very high humidity, this pencil doesn't budge. It does remove easily with facial cleanser.

reviews.headline: I will buy again
reviews.comments:
I love this pencil and got another person to buy one while I was there.  I have no eyebrows and doctor
said no permanent ones either.  I draw them on every day and have so many  comments about how
pretty my eyebrows are and who did them???  You have made my life!

reviews.headline: Never Again!
reviews.comments: I passionately hate, hate, hate these pencils. They break all the time. I ordered two minis and I rolled it up to see how much product it contained before I used one of them, and without me even touching it, 1/4" of it broke off and fell on the floor. The next one, I used three times and it broke off on the third use. It is now empty. Too dry or something. Bad pencils. Such a waste of money. I don't understand how or why people rave about these pencils. The only good thing I can say about them is that the shades are good.

reviews.headline: It is perfect to use on my brows.
reviews.comments: This is the 3rd one I've had. Since I'm lucky enough to have a natural arch to my brows this is an easy to use tool. Natural look with out the heavy designer look.

reviews.headline: I would purchase again
reviews.comments: Great product

reviews.headline: Great eyebrow product
reviews.comments: Great!

reviews.headline: Right Color, Right Texture!
reviews.comments: Very cool toned graying brows. This is the right color (if I don't get too heavy handed with the strokes). Other grays I have tried are too warm or nearly black. Not too dry, but also not waxy or greasy. Stays put all day! Ride or die status.

reviews.headline: Love it
reviews.comments: Love the color, love the convenience of color and brush in one tube. Ulta associate extremely helpful in deciding shade for my grey brows.

reviews.headline: Yes I would buy this product again.
reviews.comments: I love this eyebrow pencil. Goes on smoothly and stays on all day. I love it!

reviews.headline: Keeps Me Coming Back
reviews.comments: I used to use ABH brow pencil back in the day until this came out and I have not looked back. The shade range is amazing. It lasts all day. It's versatile. It's a little pricey for just being a pencil but it's a staple in my makeup bag!

reviews.headline: Whenever I sweat it burns my eyes. Wont use anymore.
reviews.comments: I used to not have issues but since this last year I tried it after a year of being makeup free and it's fine unless I sweat. When I sweat in the heat it burns my eyes until I take a shower. Idk if they swapped ingredients but won't use anymore .

reviews.headline: Easy application
reviews.comments: I do like that this product because it is easy to apply but it isn't truly waterproof. It does wipe off fairly easy on me.

faceoff_positive.comments: All I have to say is that if there is one thing I know - it's eyebrows. I've been obsessed with brows for like over ten years. This product is hands down, the absolute BEST eyebrow product I have ever used. The formula is light years ahead of the ABH Brow Definer. It is highly pigmented but also buildable, which is incredible. It made my light blonde, thin/sparse brows look full, defined, and perfect (in combo with Gimme Brow) and took me less than five minutes. I received this as a Platinum Perk (Thank you Benefit & Ulta, you are so good to me!) and I will be in line when Ulta opens on June 24th to purchase another one.
